{"tid":921013,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得香港樂壇，會出現關於【返工】嘅流行歌（甚至兒歌）？？","createTime":"2018-11-29T08:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T09:19:01.000Z","uid":145472,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a81b4f3a657c9eb30e742837535e04630914581b","tid":921013,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"見識少，<br />\n想知其他國家嘅流行歌有無關於【返工】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求其諗都諗到以下幾首，仲要幾hit：<br />\n容祖兒《爭氣》<br />\n關心妍《我太強》<br />\n吳浩康《擇日失戀》<br />\n呢幾首都係歌頌返工事業為上嘅中環價值。<br />\n仲有 Suppermoment《小伙子》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最離譜係麥兜，<br />\n有首《Fing Fing 下》，<br />\n關於OL 同 OT，從少教育港人要返工同OT <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（台灣我就諗到五月天《生存以上生活以下》，但係係反思返工嘅意義，唔係歌頌返工）"},{"pid":"3bb40e814d78535e842c6821443ef71fd2c3b470","tid":921013,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"蘇芮 有一首叫<br />\n休息工作再工作"},{"pid":"377c983447bb60d6c566fd04d2fb058d0972e8c5","tid":921013,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bb40e814d78535e842c6821443ef71fd2c3b470","tid":921013,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"蘇芮 有一首叫<br />\n休息工作再工作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"聽下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eddf483d703fb046ebabf01f6d8e861c1ab6741","tid":921013,"uid":13545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"邊一個發明了返工"},{"pid":"91e97c9a2844fd9504b606dedace30488ea74d8f","tid":921013,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"誰想上班"},{"pid":"8358573e218ca5827abcfe0a067181defaf410c0","tid":921013,"uid":16411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"點可以冇LMF"},{"pid":"6faa228ae9fa2fe78b68